:$\map {S_\epsilon} {a; 
orm {\,\cdot\,} } = \map { {B_\epsilon}^-} {a; 
orm {\,\cdot\,} } \setminus \map {B_\epsilon} {a; 
orm {\,\cdot\,} }$

